snippet.title: Vultures - Scavengers of Death
snippet.description:
Vultures - Scavengers of Death is a roguelike with elements of survival-horror, inspired by the classic Resident Evil game series.

Play a free demo in Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2537470/Vultures__Scavengers_of_Death

If you enjoyed the demo and want to support us, please share it with others who might like it. Also, consider subscribing to our mailing list to stay updated on the project's progress. We have plans to launch a Kickstarter campaign to bring the definitive version of the game to life.

==== L I N K S ====
Game page: https://vulturesgame.com/
Steam demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2537470/Vultures__Scavengers_of_Death
Discord: https://discord.gg/GNaCwgyfaF
